{"tid":2287403,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"為中國主導嘅學術界做好準備","createTime":"2020-11-15T17:12:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-17T07:01:11.000Z","uid":225931,"like":8,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"07db24a2e25036eefbb9ce839aa0a2ecf9979ac8","tid":2287403,"uid":225931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T17:12:49.000Z","msg":"歐美衰落趨勢好明顯 連登仔唔好再呃自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n清北排名全球第一之前 香港學術界要做好準備<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 先可以係世界佔一席位<br />\n<br />\n所有大學應該學中大同清華北京大學 甚至985 建立雙學位 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 之後人地先認你香港等同大陸水平 有開內地分校更好<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n學術界以後應該會跟ARWU排名體系<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/read.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 之後我會詳細講排名應該點玩 點做對香港有利 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔想聽唔好再睇落去 宜家左下返回鍵離開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f43ac26df900e4873f94b2e38d65d79084dbfa49","tid":2287403,"uid":370010,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T17:20:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6019da0ab3d076680ecbbd803c109d020481c325","tid":2287403,"uid":225931,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T17:23:36.000Z","msg":"ARWU 世界大學學術排名 宜家改名做 軟科上海排名Shanghai Ranking 2003年首次發表 主要特徵係全部指標都用客觀數據 而唔用聲譽問卷調查<br />\n分為6項指標:<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Hd0zfCn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHd0zfCn.jpg&h=1f3728d8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6df5bfc230001baf5adb3696e3b3c837eded1ec7","tid":2287403,"uid":68944,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T17:45:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76809971ae10c13a6f206a16cb7828aed56c89c7","tid":2287403,"uid":225931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T17:46:34.000Z","msg":"校友獲獎所有大學0分 教師獲獎得中大有分 因為有諾貝爾級數教授 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其他指標 <strong>五大</strong>( 三大 + CityU PU ) 差唔多 <br />\n<br />\n所以重點在於提升五間大學校友同教師水平<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"708a41f04907ee1eb44f792c0eb3da05513f435d","tid":2287403,"uid":225931,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T17:52:35.000Z","msg":"知彼知己百戰百勝<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 想驘人就要知點解人地升得咁快<br />\n睇番 上海排名中國榜就知上地上升秘訣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MrQjrTn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMrQjrTn.jpg&h=7493d534&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fQxRh0r.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfQxRh0r.png&h=88c017f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XFXRh0r.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXFXRh0r.jpg&h=445575a9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bce898b890d4d581c8197e075467c9579d3febb6","tid":2287403,"uid":225931,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T18:24:59.000Z","msg":"我地睇到中國嘅高等教育體系已經成熟 除左抄西方個套揀每間學校優勢學科發展<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 大量資金放入研究 最值得我地學習嘅係點培養自己人才<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n依加香港做法係用錢招兵買馬 情况唔理想 當冇錢時僱傭兵就會離開大學 減少頂級研究 到時實力一下降排名就跌 不可以持續性發展<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0decde98575583e112ac13020479fada6c9a6ad0","tid":2287403,"uid":225931,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T18:36:23.000Z","msg":"生源質量 <br />\n香港學生人數少 要提升 應該用YY Lam 嘅鯰魚效應透過引入強者 激發弱者變強<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同時要全球請優質學生<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔好睇少東歐/西非國家 獎學金全免入讀大學 不過之後至少留低大學或香港3年<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f618696d3500272a4d7e10e33db61b00db83409","tid":2287403,"uid":40521,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T18:40:33.000Z","msg":"既然自己國家啲學府咁撚勁 點解咁多支那蝗走去外國讀書嘅？"},{"pid":"8545779813617ebb720bfac2c5d70e2df375a23d","tid":2287403,"uid":225931,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T18:46:20.000Z","msg":"課程<br />\n分為勞動力型同研究型<br />\n勞動力型 以學生為顧客 提供職場所需知識同技能<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港咁細 大學應該聯合起來 開統一基礎課程節省資源 補助番一齊合作開嘅新聯合課程<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 例如之前講過city bu可以開ppe <br />\n研究型<br />\n例如ust ire hku 6688 cuhk 精研 city great <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n用jupas引多D本地生入去 學生professor 一對一咁帶佢入行<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43aca526f9b7503b8099072bb11c3b262c7c7b33","tid":2287403,"uid":225931,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T18:54:12.000Z","msg":"科創<br />\n用經紀人制 用註冊專利整產品服務 請ceo run 間公司 純利研究發明人分10%<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 大學20%於番入科創基金 其他俾公司發展<br />\n大學可以幫公司申請專利 打官司 介紹人 租地俾人 舉辦活動<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd4b3a2e260528a9f64bb6bdef469815f5088b80","tid":2287403,"uid":225931,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T19:08:13.000Z","msg":"研究<br />\n盡量留底研究型學生係本校/香港 簽死約 初期推佢做exchange scholar 之後 訂目標升到assocate professor 因為係本地培養所以請人唔使咁貴 不過一定要俾屋佢住 免租金"},{"pid":"2bfe9e5648800eda6a80a6e49221ba0db5a22008","tid":2287403,"uid":225931,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T19:18:04.000Z","msg":"內地分校<br />\n應該學科大咁同省政府傾點數<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 分校大陸學生同一般大陸學校學費一樣 模式學士勞動力型 碩士打後研究型<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同埋應該唔止一間 不限于大灣區 可以科大分校1234 開到好似ucb ucla uc system咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n勁既business school 例如ust <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 可以獨立開校區 甚至開去其他國家<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67d082f3213d988784e9893816543b9d90dbcb47","tid":2287403,"uid":225931,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T19:25:31.000Z","msg":"就業<br />\n設計課程時加埋業界 學poly咁必須intern<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有開相關學科既大學組成聯盟 同大公司傾 逼佢每年預一定位俾本地生<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"359ce3f56d4b9fa656d97093838165d4a1f27e06","tid":2287403,"uid":225931,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T19:36:17.000Z","msg":"教學<br />\n完全切割教學同研究 lecture由教師教 lab由technician教 剩返一堂比professor做enrichment lecture<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n開多D課程賺錢 例如2個課程好相似 咁俾邊個major佢取決於 偏向邊方面多D 滿足requirements就俾學生揀鐘意嘅major 名"},{"pid":"71d1640991e15f3dcc9570bbeab062244d94c973","tid":2287403,"uid":194824,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"5f618696d3500272a4d7e10e33db61b00db83409","tid":2287403,"uid":40521,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T18:40:33.000Z","msg":"既然自己國家啲學府咁撚勁 點解咁多支那蝗走去外國讀書嘅？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T20:05:03.000Z","msg":"咪就係啲支那蝗廢入唔到local u <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />得錢咪去外國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ebab77f455e087705839e986d81cabf33bd5c47","tid":2287403,"uid":62030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T05:26:16.000Z","msg":"已經贏左既習總：內循環，香港死開啦，冇利用價值喇，人才如果唔黎偉大既祖國研究，就一蚊都唔比。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z7rraK1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz7rraK1.png&h=2fcb6b41&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"884c7cc87c3614a586e79f6f862f245b5bf4b956","t